1. *Gotovi* smo sa pripremama. (We are done with the preparations.)
2. Oni su *gotovi* sa projektom. (They are done with the project.)
3. Očekujem da ću biti *gotova* sa knjigom do kraja meseca. (I am expecting to be done with the book by the end of the month.)
4. Svi su učenici *gotovi* sa zadatcima. (All the students are done with their assignments.)
5. Oni uvek završe svoj posao dovoljno brzo da budu *gotovi* pre roka. (They always finish their work quickly enough to be done before the deadline.)